###################################

 Light Log Viewer is a text viewer for viewing and analyzing 
 log files created by Java and J2EE applications.

###################################
 Author and Contact : Berlin Brown (initial release) 
 Date               : 2/17/2009
 					: updated : 7/15/2009
###################################

###################################
  Usage:
###################################

  Place the octane directory such that HOME is placed at :
  
  C:\usr\local\projects\light_logs
  
  And click on the light_logs.bat batch script.
 
  (Note: make sure that at least JRE 1.5 is installed)

Source for xhtmlrenderer:

https://xhtmlrenderer.dev.java.net/source/browse/xhtmlrenderer/